{
  "texts": [
    "Est-RoBERTa model achieved F1 0.74 for Against, 0.69 for Neutral and 0.55 for Supportive class.The misclassification was mostly between Neutral and one extreme (see Fig 2), similarly to e.g.",
    "Card et al. [16].",
    "We regard it preferable to confusing the two extremes.",
    "The results are comparable to similar studies, and there is little difference between the models.",
    "Classifier trained on an existing sentiment dataset with Est-RoBERTa achieved the worst score but performed better than expected."
  ]
}